---
const statements = [
  {
    quote: "The plan is the only lever.",
    elaboration: "You don't prompt agents individually. You write one plan.md with objectives, metrics, and constraints. Agents decompose it, execute it, and verify it. Edit the plan \u2014 agents detect the delta and replan."
  },
  {
    quote: "The oracle is the source of truth.",
    elaboration: "Not 'does the code compile?' Not 'did the agent say it's done?' The oracle runs hard metrics against actual output. 99% accuracy is either met or it isn't. No ambiguity. No hallucinated success."
  },
  {
    quote: "The system learns from its own mistakes.",
    elaboration: "When something fails, ZO doesn't just fix it \u2014 it updates the rule that allowed the failure. PRIORS.md grows with every project. The same mistake literally cannot happen twice."
  },
  {
    quote: "Zero operators means zero humans in the loop.",
    elaboration: "Humans approve the plan. Humans approve gate checkpoints. Everything between is autonomous. The name is the promise."
  }
];
---

<section id="why" data-animate>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">WHY THIS EXISTS</div>
    <h2>Why Zero Operators</h2>

    <div class="statements">
      {statements.map((s) => (
        <div class="statement" data-animate>
          <blockquote class="statement-quote">{s.quote}</blockquote>
          <p class="statement-elaboration">{s.elaboration}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  h2 {
    margin-bottom: 56px;
  }

  .statements {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 72px;
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .statement-quote {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 30px;
    line-height: 1.3;
    color: var(--amber);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--amber);
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin: 0 0 20px 0;
  }

  .statement-elaboration {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--amber-dim);
    line-height: 1.8;
    max-width: 560px;
    padding-left: 27px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .statements {
      gap: 56px;
    }

    .statement-quote {
      font-size: 24px;
      padding-left: 16px;
    }

    .statement-elaboration {
      padding-left: 19px;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
</style>
